title: Straight Up with Trent Shelton - Dropping Dec 4th
description: From the HOLLIS Network that brought you the award-winning RISE Podcast comes a new explosive audio experience from the man himself, Trent Shelton. Trent's new podcast Straight Up will explore topics designed to help you become the best version of yourself, delivered in Trent's signature soul-piercing style. Check out this trailer for a sneak preview of some of the upcoming episodes, and tune in every Wednesday for a brand new fire episode!
